<span id="freeTextContainer8784146817151669424">Loved it! A great story is one of the best gifts to give to a child. After reading The Everafter Chronicles by Casey Sean Harmon I was excited to give Casey’s adventurous book as a gift to my daughter. Filled with heartwarming action and suspense, the tale engages readers and takes them into a world where (as Casey signed in our book), ‘all things are possible!’ <br/><br/>My daughter enjoyed learning about the many different creatures in Everafter. It kept her interest and we are both looking forward to m</span>
  <span id="freeText8784146817151669424" style="display:none">Loved it! A great story is one of the best gifts to give to a child. After reading The Everafter Chronicles by Casey Sean Harmon I was excited to give Casey’s adventurous book as a gift to my daughter. Filled with heartwarming action and suspense, the tale engages readers and takes them into a world where (as Casey signed in our book), ‘all things are possible!’ <br /><br />My daughter enjoyed learning about the many different creatures in Everafter. It kept her interest and we are both looking forward to more! For me, it is especially encouraging to know she is reading a book that is promoting good lessons and values. Plus, I have to add (without giving it away as you will have to read the book to find out!), the ‘Happy Ending’ gives one of the best lessons for parents to realize! Thank-you Casey for a beautiful tale and for serving our country.<br /></span>
