<span id="freeTextContainer169244476270346624">I am a bestselling and award-winning author, and a U.S. Army SGT (Retired). I have studied with the Jerry B. Jenkins Christian Writer&apos;s Guild, and hold a degree through American Military University. My books are on a vast number of topics, simply because I&apos;m interested in so many things! I live with my wife and son in Florida.</span>
