      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/23589508-reign-of-the-night-creatures-the-everafter-chronicles-1">Quotes from Reign of the Nigh...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Clovensport, half German shepherd, half who-knows-what, was standing on hind legs before them.&rdquo;</span>
